    <item>
      <title>Rewriting PS</title>
      <link>https://concisely.co/rewriting-ps</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://concisely.co/rewriting-ps</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I believe if words can be better they should be. So the question is, can they? In the case of your website copy, I believe they can.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PS HOMEPAGE &lt;span class=&#34;subtle&#34;&gt;/ presentationstudio.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;subtle&#34;&gt;Current Copy&lt;/span&gt; V&amp;rsquo;s My Rewrites&lt;/em&gt;
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;subtle&#34;&gt;Specialising in Presentation Design &amp;amp; PowerPoint Design, we create presentations that are influential, memorable and successful.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Specialising in Presentation and PowerPoint Design we deliver messages that are memorable, influential, and successful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;subtle&#34;&gt;In an over-paced, hectic world an opportunity to communicate face to face with your audience is a rare opportunity to in advance your career and grow your company. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Whether it’s pitching for new business, motivating your sales team or giving a keynote speech, we’ll ensure your presentation is influential, memorable and successful, in three specific ways.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Welcome to XXVI — Australia’s first brand language agency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;subtle&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;b&#34;&gt;We’re putting the meaning back into words&lt;/span&gt; &lt;br&gt;Our purpose is to create deeper, more emotive connections between brands and people. Because in our eyes, words are one of the most mistreated commodities in the modern world – especially when it comes to business.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;span class=&#34;b&#34;&gt;Our words mean more&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;
Personal connections define business in today’s noisy world. Our purpose is to create deeper, more emotive connections between brands and people, and our language leads the way.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;subtle&#34;&gt;Somewhere along the way, business language was consumed by a tide of grey, redundant MBA buzzwords. Today, it’s our aim to rewrite that kind of language, and liberate words to their rightful place – to make life easier, faster, better and sometimes even funnier.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;Where grey, redundant buzzwords bore people away from brands, our concise language and consistent voice connects people to brands; deeply and emotionally. In short, our words mean more.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
