    <item>
      <title>Bonus Skills</title>
      <link>https://concisely.co/bonus-skills</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://concisely.co/bonus-skills</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Writing&amp;rsquo;s my true love but not my only skill. I have a bunch of others that afford me great insight into broader brand language puzzles and allow me to see how different pieces can compliment each other, and why, sometimes, compromises must be made.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;I Code&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I hand-built this website with some of the best tools in the business&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CloudFlare&lt;/strong&gt;: Power, protection, and encryption&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hugo&lt;/strong&gt;: A static web engine written in Go language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Github&lt;/strong&gt;: Version control and static website hosting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bootstrap&lt;/strong&gt;: A responsive, mobile-first website framework&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NB&lt;/strong&gt;: I have&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;I Optimise, Analyse, &amp;amp; Socialise&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Jack of all, master of none, I&amp;rsquo;m competent with the following tools and technologies.
&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WordPress&lt;/strong&gt;: Advanced WordPress admin, management, and hosting&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Social Media&lt;/strong&gt;: Twitter, Instagram, Hootsuite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Graphics&lt;/strong&gt;: Photoshop, Illustrator, Affinity, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Analytics&lt;/strong&gt;: Google Analytics, Webmaster Tools, Gaug.es, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Optimisation&lt;/strong&gt;: Optimizely and other A/B testing tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Website Performance&lt;/strong&gt;: Pagespeed, minification, concatenation, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Email Marketing&lt;/strong&gt;: Mailchimp and Aweber&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
